         <abstract id="aspace_12dcbd2b107806e5e6c9387af1bc4e77">Letters by Christina Rossetti to various parties, including William Bryant and Frederic James Shields. Included in a letter to William Edmonstoune Aytoun are manuscripts of six poems.</abstract>
